[114.423643, "o", "\u001b[31m╭─\u001b[0m\u001b[31m────────────────────────────────\u001b[0m\u001b[31m FailLens — 0x41df09d994b54767… \u001b[0m\u001b[31m────────────────────────────────\u001b[0m\u001b[31m─╮\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[31m│\u001b[0m \u001b[1;31m✗ Balances.InsufficientBalance\u001b[0m                                                                   \u001b[31m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[31m│\u001b[0m                                                                                                  \u001b[31m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[31m│\u001b[0m \u001b[1mWhat happened\u001b[0m                                                                                    \u001b[31m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[31m│\u001b[0m You tried to transfer more POT than the sending account holds.                                   \u001b[31m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[31m│\u001b[0m                                                                                                  \u001b[31m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[31m│\u001b[0m \u001b[1mHow to fix\u001b[0m                                                                                       \u001b[31m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[31m│\u001b[0m   1. Check the sender balance via the Portaldot explorer (portalscan.portaldot.io) or `pdk       \u001b[31m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[31m│\u001b[0m doctor`.                                                                                         \u001b[31m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[31m│\u001b[0m   2. Lower the transfer amount, or fund the account first (dev accounts are pre-funded on a      \u001b[31m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[31m│\u001b[0m --dev chain).                                                                                    \u001b[31m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[31m╰──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╯\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[121.554855, "o", "\r\n\u001b[36;1m$\u001b[0m \u001b[1mpdk explain --module 6 --error 2 --no-ai   # raw-code decoder (unique)\u001b[0m\r\n"]
