[123.436559, "o", "\u001b[36m╭─\u001b[0m\u001b[36m─────────────────────────────────────────\u001b[0m\u001b[36m pdk explain \u001b[0m\u001b[36m──────────────────────────────────────────\u001b[0m\u001b[36m─╮\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[36m│\u001b[0m \u001b[1;36mbalances.InsufficientBalance\u001b[0m                                                                     \u001b[36m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[36m│\u001b[0m                                                                                                  \u001b[36m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[36m│\u001b[0m \u001b[1mWhat it means\u001b[0m                                                                                    \u001b[36m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[36m│\u001b[0m You tried to transfer more POT than the sending account holds.                                   \u001b[36m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[36m│\u001b[0m                                                                                                  \u001b[36m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[36m│\u001b[0m \u001b[1mHow to fix\u001b[0m                                                                                       \u001b[36m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[36m│\u001b[0m   1. Check the sender balance via the Portaldot explorer (portalscan.portaldot.io) or `pdk       \u001b[36m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[36m│\u001b[0m doctor`.                                                                                         \u001b[36m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[36m│\u001b[0m   2. Lower the transfer amount, or fund the account first (dev accounts are pre-funded on a      \u001b[36m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[36m│\u001b[0m --dev chain).                                                                                    \u001b[36m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[36m╰──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╯\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[130.508356, "o", "\r\n\u001b[36;1m$\u001b[0m \u001b[1mpdk debug --demo --fix --no-ai   # diagnose AND apply the fix\u001b[0m\r\n"]
